Package com.invoices.domain

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Bank
    This Entity represents banks e.g: Bank of Cyprus, Barclays, etc..
    BankAccount
    This entity represents the MeritKapital bank accounts.
    Client
    This class represents the Client entity.
    ClientCompanyInfo
    This entity holds information about a client's company(s).
    CompanyLocation
    This entity represents the country that a given company is located at.
    Currency
    The Currency entity represents the currency that an invoice will be issued in.
    CurrencyRates
    This Entity holds the rates of currencies, for the date that an invoice was issued E.g: An invoice is issued on the 10th of July 2018, 10:00 a.m.
    CustodyCharge
    This entity represents the fee that will be paid to a MeritKapital bank account.
    Invoice
    This class represents a record in the invoices table.
    Portfolio
    The entity that represents a client's portfolio.
    ServiceProvided
    This entity represents the service that is provided to the client and for which they will be charged for.
    Vat
    This entity represents a VAT rate.
